{"tid":2203668,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小米副董事長減持套80億","createTime":"2020-09-15T13:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T03:49:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"89d838af6589a317b5ba0a5cf44f231e77b2cfc3","tid":2203668,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200915/NVBZDUIZVZALDJ4YDPVNDDR7QI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200915%2FNVBZDUIZVZALDJ4YDPVNDDR7QI%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuf4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=ad08e8c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200915%2FNVBZDUIZVZALDJ4YDPVNDDR7QI%2F&h=8df9aaa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200915/NVBZDUIZVZALDJ4YDPVNDDR7QI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n小米副董事長減持套80億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mX-pIWGmc7dAN_kT_4k23pzTgUA=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XHR4FJKRLNESFLNTKBOXWVGBSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmX-pIWGmc7dAN_kT_4k23pzTgUA%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXHR4FJKRLNESFLNTKBOXWVGBSY.jpg&h=831d7e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■小米副董事長林斌（右）連日減持；旁為集團董事長雷軍。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】小米（1810）在上月納入恒指成份股後，即遭創辦人之一、副董事長林斌出售股份，套現最多近80億元。根據外電引述銷售文件指，林斌將以每股22.55至22.85元出售3.5億股公司股票，套現78.925億至79.975億元，較昨日收市價折讓2.97%至4.25%。出售股份佔B類股票的1.99%，佔已發行股本1.45%。<br />\n<br />\n在出售後，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁售期剛過不足一個月<br />\n<br />\n林斌於去年8月21至23日，連續3日減持小米4130萬股，套現近4億元，林斌當時於新浪微博表示，「我愛小米，對小米的未來充滿信心，我相信小米模式一定能成功。」為表信心，他自願承諾一年內不會自行酌情出售其直接或間接實益擁有的公司股份。<br />\n<br />\n股價至今較其最後一次減持價升超過1.6倍，但禁售期過了不到一個月，林斌即已售出股份。據銷售文件顯示，林斌餘下持股將設有5年禁售期，即至2025年9月15日前，也不會減持股份。林斌減持小米，公司表示沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n小米昨收報23.55元，升1.29%，全日成交30.47億元，市值近5,682億元。"},{"pid":"dd7c9aa6acfe84012281577b4b2d8e81698208c6","tid":2203668,"uid":215755,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"讓領導先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c2f04eed8f75d10581b11f6daba39b1c8d0975","tid":2203668,"uid":81017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:19:12.000Z","msg":"單野唔係琴日定前日已知咩 ?"},{"pid":"e33eae1be782f8d47541200b300ab083b74ba3fb","tid":2203668,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e4e061884323b5a13143ea30cacda9240d0aaa","tid":2203668,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"Mpf 接左好多貨"},{"pid":"d02cb28f9310e844f4465a2190584c2356570174","tid":2203668,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"84312b44736ef07b3997c2cd0f3e8699de9a4533","tid":2203668,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"真正笠水狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n散戶成condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769caf80f0ac0bd7b50e6a5dd60abbe0b251e8f4","tid":2203668,"uid":325214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"禁售期一完就賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153c